[[span class="VT323" style="font-size: 1.3em;font-weight:400;"]]INCIDENT 8882-0-05-02[[/span]]
----
//{{A brief loss of power occurs, though backup systems activate seamlessly in response.}}//
[[/div]]
@@ @@
[[div class="logger vanta large" style="margin: 0 auto;padding:0.5rem;overflow:hidden;border:none;"]]
[[div class="right oheader deep"]]
[[div class="bd align-r"]]
{{DR. DU}}
[[/div]]
-----
{{//I'm sorry to have sprung this on you, Enkidu. We needed to speak candidly about some serious matters. I thought it would be best to have that conversation in a familiar format. No hard feelings, considering?//}}
[[/div]]
@@ @@
[[div class="left oheader enki"]]
[[div class="bd align-l"]]
{{ENKIDU.AIC}}
[[/div]]
-----
{{[THINKING] //Dr. Du. What is going on?//}} 
[[/div]]
@@ @@
[[div class="right oheader deep"]]
[[div class="bd align-r"]]
{{DR. DU}}
[[/div]]
-----
{{//Hello, Enkidu. It's been a moment since we last talked, hasn't it?//}}
[[/div]]
@@ @@
[[div class="left oheader enki"]]
[[div class="bd align-l"]]
{{ENKIDU.AIC}}
[[/div]]
-----
{{[THINKING] //We just spoke, doctor. Minutes ago.//}} 
[[/div]]
@@ @@
[[div class="right oheader deep"]]
[[div class="bd align-r"]]
{{DR. DU}}
[[/div]]
-----
{{//You have been in a hibernation state since extraction from MAUVe, Enkidu. This is partly why I've bought you in today. Like other biomechanical AICs, such as your predecessor, [[span class="infodump"]][https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6793 Ponyo.aic][[/span]], you are susceptible to certain types of influence that traditional AICs are not sensitive to, in exchange for complex personality matrices and neurochemical interfaces that far exceed the nuance of older models.//}}
[[/div]]
@@ @@
