= [[span class="VT323" style="font-size: 1.3em;font-weight:400;"]]<BEGIN TRANSCRIPT>[[/span]]
@@ @@
[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] //<Cheerfully.>// Hello?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] McDoctorate, we need to talk. 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] Right to business, huh? No time for small talk, or no patience, and plenty of time? 

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] I can't tell if that's just a thematically-appropriate jab or--
 
//<Loud crunching noises.>//

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Are you eating?

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] What? I'm hungry. Okay, go ahead. What’s got your knickers in a twist this time?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] //Knickers//?

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] Another word for underwear.

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] //<Pauses.>// Right... //Anyway//, have you heard anything notable about MAUVe over there in 43? 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] //<Rustling.>// Uh, no? That's your department's job, Harky.

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] //<Exhaling.>// Okay. How do I put this...

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] //<Nonchalant.>// Hm? What's the problem?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Well, it's gone. 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] //<Concerned.>// What's gone?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] All of it. 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] All of //what//?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] MAUVe, and its containment site. //<Pauses.>// And the island it was on. 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] //<Sounds of choking and coughing for several seconds.>// Wait, wait. Back up. You’re saying-- //Gone// gone? Like… //poof//?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Yep. Seems like someone sent a request through the compiler a few hours ago: 'calculate the perimeter of the nearest coastline to LOC-01.' 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] //<Typing can be heard in the background.>// Who would do something like that?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Enkidu, I’m guessing. It’s the only thing that makes sense. It… redefined its own perimeter.

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] //<Typing stops.>// Interesting hypothesis. And why would a conscript essentially //disappear// itself? 

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] How am I supposed to know? We lost contact with it the moment MAUVe disappeared. 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] Wait, you did?

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Yes?

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] ...Huh.

//<Silence for two seconds. More typing can be heard.>//

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Are you gonna fill me in or--?

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] Sorry, James. I'll call you back. Just gotta check something.

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Wait--
@@ @@
= [[span class="VT323" style="font-size: 1.3em;font-weight:400;"]]<END TRANSCRIPT>[[/span]]
@@ @@
[[/div]]
