= [[span class="VT323" style="font-size: 1.3em;font-weight:400;"]]<BEGIN TRANSCRIPT>[[/span]]
@@ @@
[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] What was that about?

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] Okay, so, good news, Enkidu.aic is still functional.

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Right. How? What happened?

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] No clue. All I know is that //Pataphysics// will be receiving measurement data from now on. 

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] That's... confusing.

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] A-ha, a few test results are already coming through. Connection's real weak, but it'll do.

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] It's not like I mind offloading it onto someone competent, but... //<Pauses.>// Should I be offended? I mean, we're cut off over here. No heads up, nothing. 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] James, you know I don’t like getting caught up in the drama of things. MAUVe’s just evolving, that’s all. It's never a been static system. Maybe it’s just… finding a more interesting conversation. I wouldn't worry about it too much.

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Hmph. 

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] I'm sure there's a perfectly reasonable explanation.

//<Silence.>//

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] Okay, reviewing the logs now, and-- //hm//.

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] What is it now?

//<No response.>//

[[span class="bd"]]DIR. HARKNESS:[[/span]] Hello...?

[[span class="bd"]]DR. MCDOCTORATE:[[/span]] I'm forwarding it to you. I need to make some more calls. Talk later.
@@ @@
= [[span class="VT323" style="font-size: 1.3em;font-weight:400;"]]<END TRANSCRIPT>[[/span]]
